How update the langs of your proyect

1. Copy the php and sh files to the parent of your directory
2. Create a update.sh file
3. Call there update_langs.sh file

Example of file:

#!/bin/bash
PWD=`pwd`
bash update.sh 1 "${PWD}/client" "php,js,tpl" "translate" "i18n" "${PWD}/client/visible/require" "http://langs" ""